1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:02,630
Sigh.

2
00:00:06,460 --> 00:00:09,380
Yuki?

3
00:00:09,380 --> 00:00:12,300
Huh? He was just here.

4
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:18,020
That was close.

5
00:00:18,020 --> 00:00:19,100
Whoa!

6
00:00:19,190 --> 00:00:20,520
Yuki?

7
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:25,360
The magazine covers and everything
are all ranking at the top...

8
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:27,070
Oh, no, you're flattering me.

9
00:00:27,070 --> 00:00:28,240
No, seriously.
The views are incredible...

10
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:31,240
By the way, about next month's...

11
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:35,200
- I was surprised too.
- Exactly.

12
00:00:35,950 --> 00:00:41,370
(He really is avoiding me, isn't he?)

13
00:00:41,370 --> 00:00:42,710
(Don't tell me...)

14
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:46,920
That's not right, Yuki.

15
00:00:48,090 --> 00:00:50,300
It's not like that.

16
00:00:58,060 --> 00:00:59,850
It's like this.

17
00:01:01,810 --> 00:01:03,400
Teacher.

18
00:01:03,980 --> 00:01:06,270
Please teach me more.

19
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,490
Not just about makeup.

20
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:11,450
But so much more...

21
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:13,790
About everything...

22
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,670
(No! This is wrong!)

23
00:01:23,670 --> 00:01:27,240
(I have to win Yuki back
on our anniversary!)

24
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:29,840
(But before that...)

25
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,340
I finally caught you.
